set said nynex spokesman robert obrien things will vary from 
one region of the country to another and i dont think we want to be 
locked into any feeling that a pattern has been set we want to 
start at the beginning 
added bellsouths terry johnson we are different companies 
facing different circumstances and what atampt and the cwa doe is 
between that company and those union members ours is a completely 
different situation as far as we are concerned 
